00:02:35.058 --> 00:02:38.356
captures a couple of things that
I've been trying to tell you,

00:02:38.356 --> 00:02:40.331
that the textbook is not the
ultimate

00:02:40.331 --> 00:02:40.846
authority.

00:02:40.846 --> 00:02:42.902
That's just what we think up
